  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to mutter-wayland</title>

    <para>
      <application>mutter-wayland</application> is the <application>wayland</application>
      compositor window manager for <application>GNOME</application>. It is not invoked 
      directly, but from <application>gnome-session</application> (on a machine with a hardware
      accelerated video driver).
    </para>

    &lfs75_checked;

